<h1><span class="namespace" title="namespace std">std::</span>streamsize</h1>
<div id="I_description">Stream size type</div>
<section id="description">
Type to represent sizes and character counts in streams.<br>
<br>
It is a <i>typedef</i> of one the fundamental signed <a href="/is_integral">integral types</a>.<br>
<br>
It is convertible to/from <samp><a href="/streamoff">streamoff</a></samp>.<br>
</section>
